data.description: Welcome to Zachary Hill Estates! This exceptional home, nestled within the renowned Zachary School District, is waiting for you! Stepping inside, you are welcomed with a grand living room featuring high ceilings and a charming wood-burning fireplace, setting the stage for cozy gatherings and tranquil moments. The kitchen features a spacious layout and convenient butler's pantry, perfect for those who love to cook or entertain. The primary bedroom offers a peaceful retreat with its ample size and a private ensuite bathroom. The property sits on an almost 1/3rd acre lot, providing ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, and more. Additionally, you'll find a versatile shed that can serve as a workshop or storage area, along with a covered carport for parking convenience. Step into the large, fenced backyard, perfect for gatherings, recreation, or relaxation. If you need a separate workspace, there's an additional shed that can easily be converted into a functional home office, ideal for remote work or creative pursuits. This property also comes with added peace of mind, featuring a BRAND-NEW ROOF and a recently updated HVAC system, just 1 year old. Not to mention this home is FLOOD X! No flood insurance is required. Don't miss the chance to make this your new home!
